<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
</head>
<body>
  <h2>Reset your password</h2>

  <p>Hi <%= @manager.email_address %>,</p>

  <p>Someone requested a password reset for your CrewControl account. Click the link below to set a new password:</p>

  <p><%= link_to "Reset my password", edit_password_reset_url(token: @token) %></p>

  <p>This link will expire in 2 hours.</p>

  <p>If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email.</p>

  <p>— The CrewControl Team</p>
</body>
</html>
